oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bobbie Moore and the Soul and Country Sounds at the Wilson County Fairgrounds
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Bobbie Moore with the Soul and Country Sounds, Boyce Hawkins, Pete Sayers and the others at the Wilson County Fairgrounds on July 4. Poster features metal photoplates of Bobbie Moore, Boyce Hawkins, and Pete Sayers.
